Sica and The Dark Princessv1.1 - I was having a boss coded for this, didn't get the boss in time; it's a level contest, not a boss contest anyways. I said I'd submit the level with or without the boss, time to live up. Enjoy the level. I hope I'm not the only one who didn't rush through making a level for this contest.

It does have cutscenes, but they're pretty short. Press START to skip cutscenes. Please forgive me for how anti-climatic it is. I'll further enhance this level in the future and maybe submit it to the hacks section as a small little thing, as it is kind of a prequel to TD4C.
